917bae8d439c4fcb478b82fe304d12024703b7b9fba85216eb9ae4d443f3858b18a7ec9be4431b31a0df386b87a42265215b7fcf79af9dfed8a0597aa5a8f866  0001-remove-backtrace_symbols.patch"
